  "body": "How to implement or use new Ref API on a custom renderer?\r\neg.\r\n```jsx\r\nlet mainCamera = React.createRef();\r\n<camera ref={mainCamera}></camera>\r\n<mouse-pad camera={mainCamera}></mouse-pad>\r\n```\r\nMy reconciler is almost simple as nothing\r\n```javascript\r\nReconciler({\r\n\tcreateInstance(type, props) {\r\n\t\tswitch (type) {\r\n\t\t\tcase 'camera':\r\n\t\t\t\treturn new FiberCamera(props);;\r\n\t\t\tcase 'mouse-pad':\r\n\t\t\t\treturn new FiberMousePad(props);\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t}\r\n        ...\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nAny tutorial ? Thanks",
